{"id":42588,"date":"2025-03-02T17:39:57","date_gmt":"2025-03-02T13:39:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=42588"},"modified":"2025-03-02T17:41:47","modified_gmt":"2025-03-02T13:41:47","slug":"counted-every-step","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/02\/counted-every-step\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Masjid: Allah counted every step as a reward"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: There was a man who lived the furthest from the mosque, as far as I know. He never missed a congregational prayer. It was said to him, \u201cIf you buy a donkey, you can ride it during the dark nights and hot days.\u201d The man said, \u201cI do not like for my house to be so close to the mosque. I want my walking towards the mosque, as well as returning to my home and family, to be recorded as good deeds for me.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Allah has gathered all of that for you.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 663<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0639\u064e\u062f\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u062c\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064f\u062e\u0652\u0637\u0650\u0626\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064c \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0642\u0650\u064a\u0